        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cellphone Jamming Reform Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill allows a state or federal correctional facility to operate a jamming system to interfere with cellphone signals within inmate housing facilities.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
